d=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fuu1665703116425.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fuu1665703116425.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fuu1665703116425.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fuu1665703116425\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     Panel Properties</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fuu1665703116425__submenu82b9cfc3-2c2f-4ba3-b1a8-4757a7209e38\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zga1665702688096.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zga1665702688096.html\" title=\"Number of available Uniface character sets (Font 0 through Font 7) for which a button is displayed when this panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are 0 through 7.\">Font Range</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ymp1665702709794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ymp1665702709794.html\" title=\"Function to include in the panel. A function can be a user-defined operation or a structure editor function, or it can represent a new line or a separator.\">Function</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uzw1665702710075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzw1665702710075.html\" title=\"Name of the glyph to be used as the icon of an operation button in a form panel. If there is a message with the same name as the glyph, it is used as the tooltip for the button.\">Glyph Name &amp; Message Text</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfq1665702709863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfq1665702709863.html\" title=\"Height of the panel button, in character cells.\">Height</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ffz1665703117029.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ffz1665703117029.html\" title=\"Text of message to be used in place of the glyph or as a tooltip. This property is read-only, displaying a message that has the same name as the selected glyph.\">Message Text</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nct1665702710006.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nct1665702710006.html\" title=\"Name of the operation activated by this button. If the operation does not exist in the form with which that this panel is associated, this button is disabled.\">Operation</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vkx1665702687952.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkx1665702687952.html\" title=\"This property determines whether buttons for character attributes (bold, italics, and underline) are displayed when the panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are True or False.\">Character Attributes</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xmm1665702688023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmm1665702688023.html\" title=\"Determines whether buttons for View, Overstrike, and Previous mode should appear in the panel when it is used as a session panel.\">View</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sag1665702709934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sag1665702709934.html\" title=\"Width of the button, in characters.\">Width</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mcf1665703117419.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mcf1665703117419.html\" title=\"Color of the panel button when it is selected and stays selected. Valid value is a web color name, system color name, or an RGB hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). (Decimal RGB colors are not supported.)\">BackColorLocked</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vry1665703117492.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vry1665703117492.html\" title=\"Color of the border when the mouse cursor rests on a panel button.\">BorderColorHover</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uab1665703117640.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uab1665703117640.html\" title=\"Color of the panel button border when the button stays depressed. A web color name, system color name, or an RGB hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). (Decimal RGB colors are not supported.)\">BorderColorLocked</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613131\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613131\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" 